@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (wp.abs((v0 + 0.53 / tmp + 0.28)) - wp.sin((tmp + 0.83 / v2 + 0.91)))
    v1 = wp.cos((tmp + (v1 + 0.78 * tmp + 0.78)))
    v2 = wp.cos(v0)
    v2 = 0.76
    v1 = (((v1 + 0.45 + tmp + 0.09) / wp.exp(v2 + 0.02)) + 0.01)
    v2 = v1
    data[tid] = v0
